description:
This is a digital collection of "Cargo" and "Reapers" taken from different published sources, most recently published in Aliens: Omnibus #5 in 2008. "Cargo" is a story taken from Dark Horse Comics: #15 and #16 published in 1993.

The story follows the misadventures of Gerald Coile, a smuggler of Alien products.

It has been reprinted as a bonus story in Aliens: Kidnapped TPB in 1999.

"Reapers" is a one-shot first published in Dark Horse Presents Fifth Anniversary Special in April 1991.

The story follows another sentient species (presumably the Reapers) hunting the Alien hive.

It has been reprinted as "Aliens: Reapers" in Dark Horse Presents: Aliens.
name: Aliens: Reapers/Cargo

description:
Welcome to...

Aria The Enchanted Collection

The Kingdom of Enchantment, a roadside theme park that flourished in the 1950s, has sat abandoned for decades. When a mysterious invitation literally drops into Kildare's lap, she is led to a remarkable discovery—a genuine magical kingdom hidden away in the Catskill Mountains. But a dark and terrible secret lies buried at the heart of this fairytale land, a reminder of the dangers of getting what you wish for.

The international award-winning story, finally brought to you in a stunning collection. Featuring the two part and hard to find ARIA: SUMMER SPELL and, as a TRUE BONUS, a never-seen-before Aria prose story written by Brian Holguin.
name: Aria: The Enchanted Collection
